Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[The serotype of the organism is not stated. With the 2 recent salmonellosis outbreaks in Texas and Arizona in August 2012, this is the 3rd prison-related foodborne outbreak reported in 4 weeks. The food vehicle has not yet been elucidated. - Mod.LL

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/1nDW.]
